     fhir:div [ fhir:v "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet tiflow-operation-outcome-details-vs</b></p><a name=\"tiflow-operation-outcome-details-vs\"> </a><a name=\"hctiflow-operation-outcome-details-vs\"> </a><p>This value set includes codes based on the following rules:</p><ul><li>Include all codes defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html\"><code>https://gematik.de/fhir/tiflow/CodeSystem/tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.0.0-ballot.2</span></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"https://gematik.de/fhir/ti/1.4.0-ballot.1/CodeSystem-operation-outcome-details-codes.html\"><code>https://gematik.de/fhir/ti/CodeSystem/operation-outcome-details-codes</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to 1.3.0, the version found through the package references\"> version ?1.3.0</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"https://gematik.de/fhir/ti/1.4.0-ballot.1/CodeSystem-operation-outcome-details-codes.html#operation-outcome-details-codes-SVC_IDENTITY_MISMATCH\">SVC_IDENTITY_MISMATCH</a></td><td>Identity mismatch: Access token or x-insurantid header does not match FHIR data (Telematik-ID / KVNR)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"https://gematik.de/fhir/ti/1.4.0-ballot.1/CodeSystem-operation-outcome-details-codes.html#operation-outcome-details-codes-SVC_VALIDATION_FAILED\">SVC_VALIDATION_FAILED</a></td><td>FHIR Profile Validation Failed</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"https://gematik.de/fhir/ti/1.4.0-ballot.1/CodeSystem-operation-outcome-details-codes.html#operation-outcome-details-codes-SVC_TELEMATIKID_TEMPORARILY_BLOCKED\">SVC_TELEMATIKID_TEMPORARILY_BLOCKED</a></td><td>The specified Telematik-ID is temporarily blocked</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"https://gematik.de/fhir/ti/1.4.0-ballot.1/CodeSystem-operation-outcome-details-codes.html#operation-outcome-details-codes-SVC_INVALID_ACCESS_TOKEN\">SVC_INVALID_ACCESS_TOKEN</a></td><td>Invalid access token provided</td></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/7.2.0/CodeSystem-operation-outcome.html\"><code>http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/operation-outcome</code></a><span title=\"Version is explicitly stated to be 4.0.0\"> version ?4.0.0</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/7.2.0/CodeSystem-operation-outcome.html#operation-outcome-MSG_RESOURCE_ID_MISMATCH\">MSG_RESOURCE_ID_MISMATCH</a></td><td>Resource Id Mismatch</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/7.2.0/CodeSystem-operation-outcome.html#operation-outcome-MSG_RESOURCE_ID_MISSING\">MSG_RESOURCE_ID_MISSING</a></td><td>Resource Id Missing</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/7.2.0/CodeSystem-operation-outcome.html#operation-outcome-MSG_RESOURCE_ID_FAIL\">MSG_RESOURCE_ID_FAIL</a></td><td>unable to allocate resource id</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/7.2.0/CodeSystem-operation-outcome.html#operation-outcome-MSG_BAD_FORMAT\">MSG_BAD_FORMAT</a></td><td style=\"color: #cccccc\">Bad Syntax: \"%s\" must be a %s'</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/7.2.0/CodeSystem-operation-outcome.html#operation-outcome-MSG_UNKNOWN_TYPE\">MSG_UNKNOWN_TYPE</a></td><td style=\"color: #cccccc\">Resource Type \"%s\" not recognised</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/7.2.0/CodeSystem-operation-outcome.html#operation-outcome-MSG_DELETED\">MSG_DELETED</a></td><td style=\"color: #cccccc\">This resource has been deleted</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/7.2.0/CodeSystem-operation-outcome.html#operation-outcome-MSG_PARAM_UNKNOWN\">MSG_PARAM_UNKNOWN</a></td><td style=\"color: #cccccc\">Parameter \"%s\" not understood</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/7.2.0/CodeSystem-operation-outcome.html#operation-outcome-MSG_BAD_SYNTAX\">MSG_BAD_SYNTAX</a></td><td style=\"color: #cccccc\">Bad Syntax in %s</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/7.2.0/CodeSystem-operation-outcome.html#operation-outcome-MSG_UNKNOWN_OPERATION\">MSG_UNKNOWN_OPERATION</a></td><td style=\"color: #cccccc\">unknown FHIR http operation</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
